metadata.name: SONDER
metadata.description:
sonder

noun: the realization that every passerby is living a life as vivid and complex as your own—populated with their own ambitions, friends, routines, worries and inherited craziness. an epic story that continues invisibly around you like an anthill sprawling deep underground, with elaborate passageways to thousands of other lives that you’ll never know existed, in which you might appear only once, as an extra texting on your phone in the background, as the blur of your silhouette coalesces with your surroundings, while a flock of pedestrians pass you by.
